# PayPal Configuration
# =====================
# Get these from https://developer.paypal.com/dashboard/applications
#
# 1. Create a PayPal Business account at https://www.paypal.com/business
# 2. Go to https://developer.paypal.com/dashboard/applications
# 3. Create a new app (or use Default Application)
# 4. Copy the Client ID and Secret from the app details
#
# For testing: Use Sandbox credentials first
# For production: Switch to Live credentials and set PAYPAL_MODE=live

# Server-side (secret — never expose to browser)
PAYPAL_CLIENT_ID=your_paypal_client_id_here
PAYPAL_CLIENT_SECRET=your_paypal_client_secret_here
PAYPAL_MODE=sandbox

# Client-side (public — safe to expose)
NEXT_PUBLIC_PAYPAL_CLIENT_ID=your_paypal_client_id_here

# Base URL for PayPal return/cancel URLs
NEXT_PUBLIC_BASE_URL=https://www.ethiocoffee.co

# WhatsApp Configuration
# Phone number in international format without + (e.g., 251911234567 for Ethiopia)
NEXT_PUBLIC_WHATSAPP_NUMBER=251911234567

# Existing variables (already configured)
# RESEND_API_KEY=your_resend_api_key
# CONTACT_EMAIL=coffee@ethiocoffee.co
# FROM_EMAIL=noreply@ethiocoffee.co
